In the recipe buffalo cauliflower  Brush the hot_sauce mixture on cauliflower and bake for an additional 20 minutes.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower bites  Cut the head of cauliflower in half.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower bites  Pluck bite-sized florets from each half.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower bites  In a medium bowl  mix the batter ingredients.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower bites  Add cauliflower to the batter.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower bites  Stir so each floret is fully coated.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower bites  Spread cauliflower florets on the baking sheet and drizzle with olive_oil.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower bites  Bake for 20 minutes.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower bites  Remove the cauliflower from the oven and toss with buffalo sauce.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower bites  Return cauliflower to oven and bake for an additional 10 minutes until browned to your liking.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower nachos  On a large baking sheet  toss together the cauliflower florets  olive_oil  paprika  salt  and pepper.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower nachos  Roast until tender  20-25 minutes.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower nachos  In a large bowl  whisk together the hot_sauce  sriracha  melted butter  and lime_juice.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower nachos  Add the roasted cauliflower to the bowl and mix to coat.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower nachos  Scatter the tortilla_chips over the baking sheet.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower nachos  Top with the cauliflower  Monterey Jack cheese  and cheddar_cheese.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower nachos  Return the baking sheet to the oven and bake until cheese is melted and bubbling  about 5 minutes.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower nachos  Top with avocado  radishes  celery  sour_cream  and cilantro.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower tacos  On a cutting board  break the head of cauliflower into florets.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower tacos  In a large mixing bowl  add flour  paprika  garlic_powder  salt  pepper  and milk  and stir until well combined.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower tacos  Add cauliflower florets to batter  making sure each piece is evenly coated.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower tacos  Transfer to a parchment paper-lined baking sheet and bake for 20 minutes  flipping halfway.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower tacos  In a small mixing bowl  combine hot_sauce  vegetable_oil  and honey  and stir until evenly combined.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower tacos  Brush hot_sauce mixture on cauliflower and bake for an additional 20 minutes.
In the recipe buffalo cauliflower tacos  Serve on warm tortillas with desired taco toppings.
In the recipe buffalo chicken dip  In a bowl  mix the chicken  cream_cheese  and buffalo sauce.
In the recipe buffalo chicken dip  Pour mixture into a cast iron skillet and smooth with a spoon.
In the recipe buffalo chicken dip  Cover with cheddar_cheese and bake for 20 minutes  or until cheese is melted and bubbly.
In the recipe buffalo chicken dip  Top with scallions and serve with your favorite chips.
In the recipe buffalo chicken football hand pies  In a large bowl  combine the chicken  salt  pepper  mozzarella_cheese  green_onions  buffalo sauce  and ranch_dressing.
In the recipe buffalo chicken football hand pies  Roll out the pie_crusts on a lightly floured surface to about 1⁄4-inch (6 mm) thick.
In the recipe buffalo chicken football hand pies  Using a paring knife  cut thin strips to resemble football laces.
In the recipe buffalo chicken football hand pies  Then  cut out small football shapes from the remaining dough.
In the recipe buffalo chicken football hand pies  Transfer 24 football shapes to the prepared baking sheet.
In the recipe buffalo chicken football hand pies  Spoon a heaping tablespoon of the chicken filling into the center of each football  leaving about a 1⁄2-inch (1 cm) border around the edges.
In the recipe buffalo chicken football hand pies  Brush the edges with egg_wash and place another football on top  pressing the edges with your finger.
In the recipe buffalo chicken football hand pies  Crimp the edges with a fork to seal.
In the recipe buffalo chicken football hand pies  Arrange the lace cutouts on top of the footballs.
In the recipe buffalo chicken football hand pies  Brush more egg_wash over the tops.
In the recipe buffalo chicken football hand pies  Bake for 15-20 minutes  or until golden brown.
In the recipe buffalo chicken football hand pies  Serve with ranch_dressing  if desired.
In the recipe buffalo chicken lettuce cups  Transfer the chicken to a cutting board and reserve at least 1⁄2 cup (120 ml) of the cooking liquid to use as chicken_broth.
In the recipe buffalo chicken lettuce cups  Using 2 forks  pull the chicken apart until shredded.
In the recipe buffalo chicken lettuce cups  In a large nonstick pan  heat the oil over medium-high heat until shimmering.
In the recipe buffalo chicken lettuce cups  Add the diced onion  diced celery  and a pinch of salt.
In the recipe buffalo chicken lettuce cups  Add the minced garlic and sauté until fragrant  about 30 seconds.
In the recipe buffalo chicken lettuce cups  Add the hot_sauce and chicken_broth.
In the recipe buffalo chicken lettuce cups  Stir until the liquid has reduced slightly  about 5 minutes.
In the recipe buffalo chicken lettuce cups  Add the shredded chicken and mix until everything is well incorporated.
In the recipe buffalo chicken lettuce wraps  In a medium bowl  add the chicken and buffalo sauce.
In the recipe buffalo chicken lettuce wraps  Stir to combine.
In the recipe buffalo chicken lettuce wraps  Add the celery  red onion  salt  and pepper.
In the recipe buffalo chicken lettuce wraps  Stir to combine and set aside.

In the recipe buffalo chicken lettuce wraps  Make the Greek yogurt ranch dressing: in a small bowl  add the Greek yogurt  dried_parsley  garlic_powder  dried_dill  onion_powder  salt  pepper  and lemon_juice.
In the recipe buffalo chicken lettuce wraps  Stir to combine.
In the recipe buffalo chicken lettuce wraps  Lay each lettuce leaf flat on a plate and scoop the chicken mixture into the middle.
In the recipe buffalo chicken lettuce wraps  Top with a spoonful of Greek yogurt ranch dressing.
In the recipe buffalo chicken lettuce wraps  Garnish with blue_cheese crumbles and sliced green onion  if desired.
In the recipe buffalo chicken mozzarella sticks  In a bowl  combine all the ingredients with a fork until smooth and evenly mixed.
In the recipe buffalo chicken mozzarella sticks  Transfer to an 8x8 inch (20x20 cm) baking dish lined with parchment paper.
In the recipe buffalo chicken mozzarella sticks  Smooth the mixture out with a spatula so that it’s evenly spread in the dish.
In the recipe buffalo chicken mozzarella sticks  Working quickly  remove the solid mixture from the sheet and cut into 4-inch x 1-inch (10 cm x 3 cm) rectangles (there should be 16).
In the recipe buffalo chicken mozzarella sticks  One by one  bread each stick by coating in flour  then dredging in egg and then bread crumbs.
In the recipe buffalo chicken mozzarella sticks  Dip once more in the egg  then once more in the bread crumbs  and transfer to a baking dish.
In the recipe buffalo chicken mozzarella sticks  Carefully lower about three or four of the coated sticks into the oil and fry for about 30 seconds  until golden brown.
In the recipe buffalo chicken mozzarella sticks  Serve warm with ranch dip.
In the recipe buffalo chicken nachos  In a bowl  mix the chicken with the hot_sauce and the ranch.
In the recipe buffalo chicken nachos  In a large pan or skillet  lay down half of the tortilla_chips  followed by half of the buffalo chicken  Monterey Jack  tomato  and green_onions.
In the recipe buffalo chicken nachos  Repeat with the remaining half of the ingredients.
In the recipe buffalo chicken nachos  Bake for 15 minutes  until cheese is melted.
In the recipe buffalo chicken onion rings  In a bowl  combine the cream_cheese  buffalo sauce  chicken  cheddar  and ranch.
In the recipe buffalo chicken onion rings  Mix with a fork until smooth and evenly mixed.
In the recipe buffalo chicken onion rings  Cut each end of the onion  peel of the papery onion skin  and cut the onion on its side into large rings.
In the recipe buffalo chicken onion rings  Separate the large slices into its separate layers.
In the recipe buffalo chicken onion rings  Put the rings on a parchment paper-lined sheet tray.
In the recipe buffalo chicken onion rings  Take the chicken mixture and press a small amount against the inside of the onion creating a ring shape of the mixture with a hole in the middle.
In the recipe buffalo chicken onion rings  Working quickly  bread each frozen ring by coating in flour  then dredge in egg and lastly in bread crumbs.
In the recipe buffalo chicken onion rings  Transfer to a baking dish.
In the recipe buffalo chicken onion rings  Carefully lower two coated rings into the oil and fry for about 3 minutes or until golden brown.
In the recipe buffalo chicken onion rings  Serve warm with blue cheese  ranch  or more buffalo sauce.
In the recipe buffalo chicken poppers  In a pan over medium heat  cook the butter and the hot_sauce until bubbly.
In the recipe buffalo chicken poppers  Toss the chicken in the sauce until evenly glazed.
In the recipe buffalo chicken potato skins  Pierce the potatoes with a fork.
In the recipe buffalo chicken potato skins  Add the potatoes to a baking sheet and bake for 60-70 minutes  until soft.
In the recipe buffalo chicken potato skins  Remove from oven and allow the potatoes to cool for at least 10 minutes.
In the recipe buffalo chicken potato skins  Cut the potatoes in half  and carefully scoop out the inside of the potatoes leaving a thin border of potato on the sides.
In the recipe buffalo chicken potato skins  Brush the insides of the potato skins with the olive_oil.
In the recipe buffalo chicken potato skins  Place the skins on the baking sheet  and bake for another 10 minutes.

In the recipe buffalo chicken potato skins  While the potatoes are baking  add the cheddar cheese  mozzarella  cream_cheese  shredded chicken  ranch seasoning and hot_sauce in a bowl  and gently mix them together.
In the recipe buffalo chicken potato skins  Fill each potato skin with the mixture  and then top each potato with reserved sharp cheddar cheese.
In the recipe buffalo chicken potato skins  Bake the potato skins for about 15 minutes  or until cheese is browned and crispy.
In the recipe buffalo chicken potato skins  Remove from oven and garnish with your favorite white dressing and chives (optional).
In the recipe buffalo chicken potstickers  In a large bowl mix together shredded chicken  celery  carrots  cream_cheese  and hot sauce.
In the recipe buffalo chicken potstickers  To form the potstickers scoop about a teaspoon amount into the center of a wrapper.
In the recipe buffalo chicken potstickers  Wet your finger and brush the top edge of the wrapper with water.
In the recipe buffalo chicken potstickers  Fold the wrapper in half and press and crimp the edges to close.
In the recipe buffalo chicken potstickers  Place the potstickers seam side up into the hot oil and leave to brown (once placed DO NOT MOVE - you want a nice golden brown on the bottom  right?
In the recipe buffalo chicken potstickers  After about two minutes  or until desired color is reached  add the water and cover the saucepan.
In the recipe buffalo chicken potstickers  Uncover  remove from pan and serve with your choice of ranch or blue cheese dipping sauce.
In the recipe buffalo chicken sliders  Carefully slice the pack of dinner_rolls in half  being sure to keep the rolls connected as a single units as they are split into tops and bottoms.
In the recipe buffalo chicken sliders  Remove the top and place the bottom section in a 9x12 inch (23x30 cm) baking dish.

In the recipe buffalo chicken sliders  Sprinkle the bottom with about 1 cup (100 g) of the shredded mozzarella_cheese (make sure it is evenly coated as this will act as a barrier between the sauce and the bread  preventing the rolls from getting soggy).
In the recipe buffalo chicken sliders  Top the cheese with the shredded rotisserie chicken.
In the recipe buffalo chicken sliders  Drizzle the hot_sauce and ranch_dressing evenly over the chicken and spread out evenly with a spoon.
In the recipe buffalo chicken sliders  Top with remaining mozzarella_cheese.
In the recipe buffalo chicken sliders  Place the top half of the rolls on top and brush evenly with melted butter.
In the recipe buffalo chicken sliders  Bake in a preheated oven for 20-25 minutes  until the cheese is melty and the rolls have heated through.
In the recipe buffalo chicken sliders  Remove from oven  cool slightly before transferring to a cutting board.
In the recipe buffalo chicken sliders  Using a large knife  follow the lines of the rolls  cutting them into 12 individual sliders.
In the recipe buffalo chicken stuffed sweet potato  Using a fork  poke holes in the top of the sweet_potato.
In the recipe buffalo chicken stuffed sweet potato  Microwave on high for 10 minutes.
In the recipe buffalo chicken stuffed sweet potato  Drizzle with buffalo sauce and toss until well coated.
In the recipe buffalo chicken stuffed sweet potato  In a bowl  add the Greek yogurt  chopped green_onion  salt  and black pepper and stir to combine.
In the recipe buffalo chicken stuffed sweet potato  Cut sweet_potato open lengthwise and fill with buffalo chicken  then top with crema and garnish with sliced green_onions.
In the recipe buffalo chicken toaster quesadilla  Using a butter knife  spread the cream_cheese in an even layer over the tortilla.
In the recipe buffalo chicken toaster quesadilla  Add the chicken to the top half of the tortilla.
In the recipe buffalo chicken toaster quesadilla  Sprinkle with scallions.
In the recipe buffalo chicken toaster quesadilla  Fold the tortilla in half from the bottom  then fold in the sides  being careful not to tear the tortilla.
In the recipe buffalo chicken toaster quesadilla  Toast on medium-high  until golden brown.
In the recipe buffalo chicken totchos  Arrange tater tots on a 11x17 inch (28x43 cm) nonstick baking sheet.
In the recipe buffalo chicken totchos  Bake the tater tots according to package directions  about 20-25 minutes  flipping halfway.
In the recipe buffalo chicken totchos  In a mixing bowl  season chicken lightly with a pinch of salt and pepper.
In the recipe buffalo chicken totchos  Add the green_onions and buffalo sauce.
In the recipe buffalo chicken totchos  Mix well and keep warm.
In the recipe buffalo chicken totchos  In a pot  combine cheddar cheese and cornstarch.
In the recipe buffalo chicken totchos  Stir until cheese is well coated with the cornstarch.
In the recipe buffalo chicken totchos  Set the saucepan set over medium heat  adding in evaporated_milk and buffalo sauce.
In the recipe buffalo chicken totchos  Bring sauce to simmer  whisking constantly until cheese has melted and sauce has thickened  about 5-8 minutes.
In the recipe buffalo chicken totchos  Stirring occasionally to prevent burning.
In the recipe buffalo chicken totchos  To assemble totchos  layer tater tots followed by the cheese sauce and buffalo chicken onto your serving platter.
In the recipe buffalo chicken totchos  Garnish with blue_cheese_dressing  remaining buffalo sauce  bacon and remaining green_onions.

In the recipe buffalo chickpea sliders  In a large bowl  combine the chickpeas  buffalo sauce  vegan_mayonnaise  garlic_powder  onion_powder  salt  and pepper and mash well with a fork or potato masher until the mixture has a chunky consistency.

In the recipe buffalo chickpea sliders  To make the ranch dressing  combine vegan_mayonnaise  almond_milk  apple_cider_vinegar  lemon_juice  garlic_powder  onion_powder  paprika  salt  pepper  parsley  and dill
In the recipe buffalo chickpea sliders  Use a large bread knife to cut the whole sheet of slider buns in half crosswise.
In the recipe buffalo chickpea sliders  Remove the top and set aside.
In the recipe buffalo chickpea sliders  Spread the buffalo chickpea mixture on the bottom half of the slider buns  then top with lettuce  tomato  and red_onion.
In the recipe buffalo chickpea sliders  Drizzle the ranch dressing over the top.
In the recipe buffalo chickpea sliders  Place the top half of the slider buns back on top.
In the recipe buffalo chickpea sliders  Then slice between the buns to make 12 sliders.
In the recipe buffalo chickpea wraps  In a large saucepan  heat the olive_oil over medium heat.
In the recipe buffalo chickpea wraps  Once the oil begins to shimmer  add the chickpeas and cook until lightly browned  2-3 minutes.
In the recipe buffalo chickpea wraps  Add the garlic_powder  salt  and buffalo sauce and cook for 2 more minutes  until the sauce thickens and the chickpeas have browned.
In the recipe buffalo chickpea wraps  Set aside.
In the recipe buffalo chickpea wraps  In a small bowl or liquid measuring cup  combine the hummus  lemon_juice  and water and whisk thoroughly.
In the recipe buffalo chickpea wraps  To assemble a wrap  top a tortilla with romaine  chickpeas  tomatoes  and red_onion  then pour on the dressing.
In the recipe buffalo chickpea wraps  Fold in the sides of the wrap and roll up like a burrito.
In the recipe buffalo chickpea wraps  Cut in half.
In the recipe buffalo meatball corn dogs  Meatballs: In a medium bowl  mix together ground_chicken  bread crumbs  egg  blue_cheese  salt  pepper  and Frank’s Red Hot until evenly combined.
In the recipe buffalo meatball corn dogs  Be careful not to overmix.
In the recipe buffalo meatball corn dogs  Roll into golf-size balls.
In the recipe buffalo meatball corn dogs  Heat olive_oil in a skillet over medium heat.
In the recipe buffalo meatball corn dogs  Add meatballs and cook until brown on all sides  about 3–4 minutes per side.
In the recipe buffalo meatball corn dogs  Batter: Whisk together cornmeal  flour  salt  sugar  and baking_powder.
In the recipe buffalo meatball corn dogs  Add in egg and milk  then whisk until a smooth batter forms.
In the recipe buffalo meatball corn dogs  Place the meatballs on skewers  lollipop-style.
In the recipe buffalo meatball corn dogs  Holding onto the skewer  dip the meatball into the batter.
In the recipe buffalo meatball corn dogs  Lower the meatballs into the oil and cook for 3–4 minutes  until the meatballs are cooked through and the outsides are a deep golden brown.
In the recipe buffalo meatball corn dogs  Serve with more Frank’s and ranch_dressing for dipping.
In the recipe buffalo popcorn  In a small bowl  mix together the paprika  cayenne  and salt.
In the recipe buffalo popcorn  Set aside.
In the recipe buffalo popcorn  In a separate small bowl  mix together the sugar  hot_sauce  and olive_oil.
In the recipe buffalo popcorn  Set aside.
In the recipe buffalo popcorn  Melt the coconut_oil in a large pot over medium heat.
In the recipe buffalo popcorn  Add 3-4 popcorn kernels and cover with the lid.
In the recipe buffalo popcorn  Once they pop  add the rest of the kernels and cover  shaking every 10 seconds  until they begin pop.
In the recipe buffalo popcorn  Once the pops are more than 3 seconds apart  turn off the heat and let sit for 15 seconds to allow any final kernels to pop.
In the recipe buffalo popcorn  Uncover and drizzle the hot_sauce mixture over the popcorn.
In the recipe buffalo popcorn  Carefully toss to coat.
In the recipe buffalo popcorn  Sprinkle the spice mixture over the popcorn and stir to coat evenly.
In the recipe buffalo popcorn  Transfer to a bowl and eat immediately  or spread in a single layer on a baking sheet and let cool completely before storing in a sealed container for up to 2 days.
In the recipe build your own pizza  Cut the tortilla into smaller circles.
In the recipe build your own pizza  Pack with cheese  ham  and a hard-boiled egg separately.
In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  Make the lemongrass chili oil: Chop the bottom 4 inches (10 cm) from the lemongrass stalks and discard the tops.
In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  Peel off any tough outer layers and discard  then thinly slice the remaining lemongrass.
In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  Process the sliced lemongrass in a food processor until very finely minced.
In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  In a large enameled Dutch oven  heat the canola_oil over high heat until it reaches 300°F (150°C).

In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  Add the garlic and lemongrass to the hot oil and cook until the garlic is golden brown and aromatic  about 10 minutes.
In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  Add the shallots.
In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  Reduce the heat to very low and add the red_pepper_flakes.
In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  Cook until extremely aromatic  about 2 minutes.
In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  Add the fish_sauce  sugar  and water.

In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  Continue cooking for 2 hours  stirring occasionally to prevent the garlic from scorching at the bottom  until the oil has turned red.
In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  In a small pot  combine the sugar  vinegar  water  garlic and salt.
In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  Bring to a simmer over medium heat and stir until the sugar dissolves.
In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  Make the steak: Rub the steak with the rice_bran_oil and sprinkle salt on both sides.

In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  Sear the steak in the hot skillet until the internal temperature reaches 130–135°F (54–57°C) for medium-rare  6–10 minutes  turning the steak
In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  Remove the steak from the skillet and let rest for 10 minutes  then slice thinly against the grain.
In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  To serve  add the rice noodles to a wide  shallow dish.
In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  Arrange the lettuce  basil  mint  pickles  fried_shallots  and peanuts on top.
In the recipe bun bo xa ot vietnamese steak and rice noodle salad as made by diep  Arrange the beef on top and spoon over some nuoc cham and lemongrass chili oil.".
In the recipe bunny shaped apple slices  Cut the apple into 6 wedges.
In the recipe bunny shaped apple slices  Remove the core and seeds.
In the recipe bunny shaped apple slices  To create the ears: Using a paring knife  make two intersecting slits about 3⁄4 of the way down the skin side of each apple slice.
In the recipe bunny shaped apple slices  Soak the apple wedges in salt_water or lemon water until ready to eat.
In the recipe burrito cups  Fry the onion until translucent.
In the recipe burrito cups  Add the chicken and fry until white.
In the recipe burrito cups  Add the garlic cloves and fry for 2 minutes.
In the recipe burrito cups  Remove from heat and transfer mix to a bowl.
In the recipe burrito cups  Mix in the diced tomato and burrito spice mix.
In the recipe burrito cups  Stir until completely covered.
In the recipe burrito cups  Place the six tortillas on top of each other.
In the recipe burrito cups  Cut into a square and then cut into quarters.
In the recipe burrito cups  In an oiled muffin tin  place the first layer of tortilla squares in and push down.
In the recipe burrito cups  Push the other layers of tortilla on top of these in a star formation.
In the recipe burrito cups  Spread refried_beans on the bottom of each tortilla  then the cooked_rice  then the chicken mix  then top with grated cheddar_cheese.
In the recipe burrito cups  Serve with sour_cream  guacamole  salsa  and coriander.
In the recipe burrito stuffed chicken rollups  Add a tablespoon of olive_oil to a skillet over medium-high heat.
In the recipe burrito stuffed chicken rollups  Once the oil begins to shimmer  add the onion  bell_peppers  jalapenos  garlic  salt  and pepper.
In the recipe burrito stuffed chicken rollups  Cook  stirring occasionally  until golden brown and caramelized  about 15 minutes.
In the recipe burrito stuffed chicken rollups  Set aside to cool
In the recipe burrito stuffed chicken rollups  Place 4 chicken_breasts in a bowl near a wide work surface.
In the recipe burrito stuffed chicken rollups  Combine the salt  pepper  paprika  oregano  cumin  garlic_powder in a small bowl  and mix together with a fork.
In the recipe burrito stuffed chicken rollups  Pour half of the spice mixture onto the chicken  set the other half aside to use later.
In the recipe burrito stuffed chicken rollups  Rub all the spices onto the chicken until completely coated.

In the recipe burrito stuffed chicken rollups  To pound out the chicken  first take a chicken_breast and butterfly it by slicing half way into it to open it like a book  making sure not to slice it all the way through.
In the recipe burrito stuffed chicken rollups  Cover the breast with parchment paper or plastic wrap.
In the recipe burrito stuffed chicken rollups  Gently pound the meat with a mallet or rolling pin until it is evenly flattened  about 1⁄4 inch (6 mm) in thickness.

In the recipe burrito stuffed chicken rollups  Onto each pounded chicken_breast  rub on about 2 tablespoons refried beans  1 tablespoon chopped tomatoes  1 tablespoon cotija cheese  and 1 tablespoon cooked black_beans.
In the recipe burrito stuffed chicken rollups  Carefully roll the chicken_breast until the ends overlap and then place the chicken into a greased baking dish.

In the recipe burrito stuffed chicken rollups  For the chipotle sauce  add the tomato_sauce  chipotle_peppers  tomato_paste  lime_juice  and the remaining spice mixture to a blender and puree until smooth.
In the recipe burrito stuffed chicken rollups  Pour the sauce over the cooked chicken roll ups and sprinkle with more cotija cheese.
In the recipe burrito stuffed chicken rollups  Serve with cooked_rice  avocado  sour_cream  and/or pico_de_gallo.
In the recipe butter chicken mac n cheese  Melt the butter in a large skillet over medium high heat until melted.
In the recipe butter chicken mac n cheese  Add the chicken  salt  and pepper.
In the recipe butter chicken mac n cheese  Fry for about 5-8 minutes or until cooked through.
In the recipe butter chicken mac n cheese  Take out and set aside.
In the recipe butter chicken mac n cheese  Add the onion and fry for 2 minutes.
In the recipe butter chicken mac n cheese  Stir in the flour.
In the recipe butter chicken mac n cheese  Gradually whisk in the milk.
In the recipe butter chicken mac n cheese  Whisk in the butter chicken sauce.
In the recipe butter chicken mac n cheese  Whisk in the mozzarella and cheddar_cheese.
In the recipe butter chicken mac n cheese  Once the cheese has melted into the mixture  stir in the chicken and elbow pasta.
In the recipe butter chicken mac n cheese  Sprinkle on some more cheese on top.
In the recipe butter chicken mac n cheese  Bake in the oven for 15 minutes  until the cheese is brown and bubbling on top.
In the recipe butter chicken mac n cheese  Garnish with coriander.
In the recipe butter chicken meatballs  Meatballs: In a medium bowl  stir together bread crumbs and milk.
In the recipe butter chicken meatballs  Add in garlic  egg  salt  and pepper  then stir until well-combined.
In the recipe butter chicken meatballs  Stir in ground_chicken.
In the recipe butter chicken meatballs  With oiled hands  roll the meat into golf-size balls.
In the recipe butter chicken meatballs  Pour 1 tablespoon vegetable_oil into a skillet over medium heat.
In the recipe butter chicken meatballs  Add meatballs and brown on all sides.
In the recipe butter chicken meatballs  Sauce: Heat vegetable_oil and butter in the same skillet over medium heat.
In the recipe butter chicken meatballs  Add onions and sauté until translucent  about 5 minutes.
In the recipe butter chicken meatballs  Add garlic and ginger  then let sizzle for a minute or two
In the recipe butter chicken meatballs  Blend sauce until smooth  adding a tablespoon or two of water if it is too thick to blend.
In the recipe butter chicken meatballs  Pour the sauce back into the skillet.
In the recipe butter chicken meatballs  Whisk in the butter  cream  and 1 teaspoon garam_masala.
In the recipe butter chicken meatballs  Add the meatballs to the sauce and stir to coat.
In the recipe butter chicken meatballs  Cover and cook for 5 minutes  or until meatballs are fully cooked through.
In the recipe butter chicken meatballs  Garnish with cilantro.
In the recipe butter cookies  In a large bowl  combine the butter and sugar.
In the recipe butter cookies  Cream together with an electric hand mixer until the butter is light and fluffy
In the recipe butter cookies  Add the egg and milk  and continue beating until smooth.
In the recipe butter cookies  In medium bowl  stir together the flour  baking_soda  and salt.
In the recipe butter cookies  Gradually add the dry ingredients to the wet ingredients and beat to combine until the dough comes together.
In the recipe butter cookies  Turn the dough out onto a lightly floured surface and roll out to 1⁄4-inch (3⁄4 cm) thick.
In the recipe butter cookies  Cut out shapes with cookie cutters of your choice.
In the recipe butter cookies  Transfer the cookies to the prepared baking sheet  spacing about 1 inch (2.5 cm) apart.
In the recipe butter cookies  Bake for 6-8 minutes  or until the cookies are firm around the edges but still soft at the centers.
In the recipe butter cookies  Make the frosting: In a large bowl  combine the powdered_sugar  butter  vanilla  and condensed_milk.
In the recipe butter cookies  Beat with an electric hand mixer until creamy and smooth.
In the recipe butter cookies  Decorate the cookies with the frosting  sprinkles  and candies.
In the recipe butter lava cake  To make the cake batter  whisk together the flour  baking_powder  and salt in a medium bowl.
In the recipe butter lava cake  In a large bowl  use a hand mixer to cream the butter and sugar until fluffy.
In the recipe butter lava cake  Mix in the egg and vanilla_extract.
