In the recipe cheesy potato pancakes  Add the grated potatoes and grated onion onion to a large bowl.
In the recipe cheesy potato pancakes  Add in the eggs  garlic  cornstarch  salt  pepper  cheddar_cheese  monterey jack  and breadcrumbs and mix until combined.
In the recipe cheesy potato pancakes  Take 1⁄2 cup of the potato mixture and form into a thin patty  about 1⁄3-inch thick.
In the recipe cheesy potato pancakes  Heat cooking oil over medium-high heat and place potato patty into the skillet.
In the recipe cheesy potato pancakes  Cook for 3-5 minutes on each side  or until golden brown and crispy on the outside.
In the recipe cheesy potato pancakes  Serve with sour_cream and green_onions on top  and enjoy!
In the recipe cheesy pretzel ring dip  Cut pizza_dough into 12 portions.
In the recipe cheesy pretzel ring dip  Roll into balls.
In the recipe cheesy pretzel ring dip  Boil water and add baking_soda.
In the recipe cheesy pretzel ring dip  Place dough balls in the pot  boiling for 20-30 seconds in batches.
In the recipe cheesy pretzel ring dip  Line a 10” (25 cm) skillet with the dough balls  making a ring along the outside edge.
In the recipe cheesy pretzel ring dip  Par-bake the dough for 15 minutes.
In the recipe cheesy pretzel ring dip  While the dough is baking  combine the cream_cheese  11⁄2 cups (150 g) of cheddar  sour_cream  cayenne_pepper  and garlic_powder until smooth.
In the recipe cheesy pretzel ring dip  Fill the center of the dip ring with the cheese dip.
In the recipe cheesy pretzel ring dip  Top the dip and the dough balls with the remaining cheddar.
In the recipe cheesy pretzel ring dip  Bake for an additional 10-15 minutes (or until the pretzel balls have browned and the dip has fully melted).
In the recipe cheesy pretzel ring dip  Allow to cool before serving.
In the recipe cheesy scalloped potatoes  Thinly slice the potatoes into rounds about 1⁄8-inch (3 mm) thick.
In the recipe cheesy scalloped potatoes  Submerge in a large bowl of water to keep from browning and set aside.
In the recipe cheesy scalloped potatoes  In a medium pot over low heat  melt the butter.
In the recipe cheesy scalloped potatoes  Once the butter begins to foam  add the garlic and cook for 2-3 minutes  until fragrant.
In the recipe cheesy scalloped potatoes  Add the flour and stir until flour and butter resemble the consistency of wet sand  creating a roux.
In the recipe cheesy scalloped potatoes  While stirring continuously  add the non-dairy milk  vegetable_broth  salt  and pepper and bring to a boil.
In the recipe cheesy scalloped potatoes  Stir in the nutritional_yeast and continue to cook for 2-3 minutes  or until the sauce thickens.
In the recipe cheesy scalloped potatoes  In a medium baking dish  add 2 layers of the sliced potatoes  followed by a layer of the sliced onions.
In the recipe cheesy scalloped potatoes  Pour on half of the cheese sauce and spread with a spatula to coat all of the potatoes and onions.
In the recipe cheesy scalloped potatoes  Add another 2 layers of potatoes and pour on the remaining cheese sauce.
In the recipe cheesy scalloped potatoes  Cover with a lid or foil and bake for 1 hour.
In the recipe cheesy scalloped potatoes  Then  uncover and bake for 10-15 minutes more  until the top is golden and bubbling and the potatoes are tender.
In the recipe cheesy scalloped potatoes  Garnish with parsley and serve warm.
In the recipe cheesy spinach and artichoke bread ring dip  Coat a 10 inch (25cm) oven-safe skillet with olive_oil.
In the recipe cheesy spinach and artichoke bread ring dip  Place the dinner roll dough balls in a ring around the skillet.
In the recipe cheesy spinach and artichoke bread ring dip  Cover and let rise until thawed and doubled in size.

In the recipe cheesy spinach and artichoke bread ring dip  In a medium bowl  combine cream_cheese  parmesan  romano  mozzarella  sour_cream  artichoke hearts  spinach  garlic  basil  and red_pepper flakes.
In the recipe cheesy spinach and artichoke bread ring dip  Once the dough has thawed  uncover and scoop the dip into the center of the skillet.
In the recipe cheesy spinach and artichoke bread ring dip  Brush the rolls with olive_oil  and top with an additional sprinkle of cheese (optional).
In the recipe cheesy spinach and artichoke bread ring dip  Bake in a preheated oven at 375 ̊F (190 ̊C) for 25 minutes.
In the recipe cheesy spinach and artichoke bread ring dip  Remove and let cool slightly before serving.
In the recipe cheesy taco breadsticks  Sauté onions and garlic until transparent.
In the recipe cheesy taco breadsticks  Add the ground_beef and taco_seasoning.
In the recipe cheesy taco breadsticks  Cook until browned.
In the recipe cheesy taco breadsticks  Remove from heat and set aside.

In the recipe cheesy taco breadsticks  On a floured surface  cut the pizza_dough into 5 strips and place spoonfuls of the beef mixture into the middle of each strip  followed by the Mexican cheese blend.
In the recipe cheesy taco breadsticks  Fold and pinch the dough around the cheese and meat along the entire strip  ensuring to close off the ends.
In the recipe cheesy taco breadsticks  Brush each breadstick with olive_oil and transfer to a baking sheet.
In the recipe cheesy taco breadsticks  Remove from the oven and top each breadstick with more cheese.
In the recipe cheesy taco breadsticks  Enjoy!
In the recipe cheesy taquitos chequitos  In a large saucepan over medium heat  brown the ground_beef.
In the recipe cheesy taquitos chequitos  Once the beef is browned  add the onion and garlic.
In the recipe cheesy taquitos chequitos  Cook until the onion is translucent  about 5 minutes.
In the recipe cheesy taquitos chequitos  Add the salt  cumin  chili_powder  cayenne  paprika  and oregano.
In the recipe cheesy taquitos chequitos  Cook for 2-3 minutes more to allow the flavors to meld and ensure the beef is cooked through.
In the recipe cheesy taquitos chequitos  In a clean large saucepan over medium heat  combine the shredded chicken and crushed tomatoes.
In the recipe cheesy taquitos chequitos  Add the salt  cumin  chili_powder  cayenne  paprika  and oregano.
In the recipe cheesy taquitos chequitos  Cook until warmed through  about 5 minutes.
In the recipe cheesy taquitos chequitos  In a medium bowl  mix together the Parmesan and Mexican-blend cheeses.
In the recipe cheesy taquitos chequitos  Add about 1⁄4 cup (25 G) of cheese to the center of the pan and spread into a circle.
In the recipe cheesy taquitos chequitos  Let the cheese melt  then add a spoonful of beef or chicken filling to the bottom of the circle.
In the recipe cheesy taquitos chequitos  Slide the cheese shell out of the pan onto a cutting board and let cool for 30 seconds  then roll tightly to encase the filling.
In the recipe cheesy taquitos chequitos  The melted cheese should stick to the outside  sealing the taquito.
In the recipe cheesy taquitos chequitos  Repeat with the remaining ingredients.
In the recipe cheesy taquitos chequitos  Serve the taquitos with lime_wedges  sour_cream  and fresh_cilantro.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Make the beef: Heat the vegetable_oil in a large skillet over medium heat.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Add the onion and cook until translucent  about 5 minutes.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Add the garlic and cook for 1-2 minutes more  until softened but not browned.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Add the beef  cumin  chili_powder  oregano  salt  and pepper to the pan.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Stir to break up the ground_beef  then let sit undisturbed for about 3 minutes to let the meat brown.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Stir and continue cooking until no pink remains  5-7 minutes total.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Add 2 tablespoons of the pickled jalapeño liquid and cook until slightly evaporated  about 1 minute.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Drain any excess liquid from beef and set aside.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Make the wontons: In a medium bowl  mix together the American cheese and beef until well combined with large chunks of cheese still intact.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  On a clean work surface  lay out 10 wonton_wrappers at a time.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Scoop about 2 teaspoons of the beef mixture into the center of each wonton wrapper.

In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Lightly brush 2 edges of the wrapper with egg  then fold up one corner to meet the opposite corner  forming a triangle  and gently press all the edges together to seal  ensuring all the air is pressed out from around the filling.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Working in batches  gently lower 4-6 filled wontons into the hot oil.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Fry until golden brown  flipping once  2-3 minutes total.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Transfer to the wire rack to drain and sprinkle lightly with salt.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Arrange half of the stuffed wontons on a baking sheet.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Cover with 1⁄2 cup (50 g) of the shredded cheddar and about half the black_beans.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Top with the remaining wontons and cheddar cheese.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Broil the wontons until the cheese is melted and bubbly  about 2 minutes.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Top the wonton nachos with the remaining black_beans  jalapeños  red onion  tomato  sour_cream  avocado  and cilantro.
In the recipe cheesy wonton nachos  Serve with lime_wedges on the side.
In the recipe cheesy zucchini sticks  Grate zucchini into a medium bowl.
In the recipe cheesy zucchini sticks  Transfer grated zucchini into a large bowl and add parmesan_cheese  garlic_powder  pepper  red_pepper_flakes  salt  and egg.
In the recipe cheesy zucchini sticks  Mix together.
In the recipe cheesy zucchini sticks  Pour the mixture onto a small towel and wring the excess fluid from mix.
In the recipe cheesy zucchini sticks  Place a piece of parchment paper on a baking sheet and spread mixture evenly into a square about a 1⁄2-inch (1cm) thick.
In the recipe cheesy zucchini sticks  Bake for 35-40 minutes or until middle has thickened.
In the recipe cheesy zucchini sticks  Remove from oven and spread cheddar and mozzarella_cheese over top.
In the recipe cheesy zucchini sticks  Place back in the oven at 350oF (180oC) for 10 more minutes or until cheese melts and is bubbling.
In the recipe cheesy zucchini sticks  Let cool for 5 minutes  then cut.
In the recipe cheesy zucchini sticks  Serve with marinara  ranch  or any sauce of your choosing!
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Break down the chicken into 6 parts--2 thighs  2 breasts  and 2 wings.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Add the chicken pieces to large bowl with the Worcestershire sauce  2 tablespoons of canola_oil  the salt  and pepper and toss to coat.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  In a large pan over medium-high heat  add the chicken  skin-side down  and the remaining tablespoon of oil.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Sear the chicken until browned on both sides and the skin is crispy  about 5-8 minutes per side.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Remove the chicken from the pan and set aside.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  To the hot pan  add the onion  celery  green chiles  garlic  and tomato_paste  stirring to combine after each ingredient is added.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Deglaze the pan with the beer and chicken_stock.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Return the chicken to pan  cover  reduce the heat to medium-low  and braise for 1 hour.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Make the pico de gallo: In a large bowl  combine the tomatoes  onions  jalapeño  salt  cilantro  and the lime zest and juice.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Stir to combine.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Make the avocado yogurt: In a large bowl  combine the yogurt  avocados  lemon_juice  salt  pepper  and olive_oil.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Mash with 2 forks until mostly smooth and well combined.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Remove the chicken from the braising liquid.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Increase the heat to high and cook the braising liquid until reduced by half  about 30 minutes.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Using forks  shred the chicken and place the meat in a large bowl.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Discard the bones or save for another use.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Add 1 cup (240 ML) of the reduced braising liquid to the chicken and stir to combine.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Assemble the nachos: Spread the plantain_chips on a baking sheet in an even layer.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Top with half of the black_beans and all of the chicken  then the remaining black_beans.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Cover with the cheddar  mozzarella  and pepper Jack cheeses and finish with the pickled jalapeños.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Bake for 10-15 minutes  or until the cheese is melted.
In the recipe chef jjs plantain nachos  Top the nachos with the pico de gallo  avocado yogurt  and cilantro.
In the recipe cherry blossom raindrop cake  Make the cherry blossom jelly: In a small bowl  combine the agar and sugar.
In the recipe cherry blossom raindrop cake  Pour the water into a small pan  then add the agar mixture and stir.
In the recipe cherry blossom raindrop cake  Cook over high heat until the water is boiling.
In the recipe cherry blossom raindrop cake  Reduce the heat to low and cook for 2 minutes.
In the recipe cherry blossom raindrop cake  Move the pan to the ice bath  and chill for 3 minutes  stirring occasionally.
In the recipe cherry blossom raindrop cake  In an ice ball tray  place the cherry blossoms in the bottom and pour the agar-sugar mixture over them.
In the recipe cherry blossom raindrop cake  Chill for 15 minutes.
In the recipe cherry blossom raindrop cake  Make the milk jelly: In a small bowl  combine the agar and sugar.
In the recipe cherry blossom raindrop cake  Pour the milk into a small pan  then add agar mixture and stir.
In the recipe cherry blossom raindrop cake  Cook over high heat until the milk is simmering.
In the recipe cherry blossom raindrop cake  Reduce to the heat to low and cook for 2 minutes.
In the recipe cherry blossom raindrop cake  Move the pan to the ice bath and chill for 2 minutes.
In the recipe cherry blossom raindrop cake  Pour the milk mixture over the chilled cherry blossom layer in the ice ball tray.
In the recipe cherry blossom raindrop cake  Cover with the lid and chill for 1 hour.
In the recipe cherry blossom raindrop cake  Remove the raindrop cake from the tray  and pour the brown sugar_syrup over it.
In the recipe cherry clafoutis  Pit the cherries by placing them on top of an empty glass bottle  one at a time.
In the recipe cherry clafoutis  Using a chopstick  push through the cherry to remove the pit.
In the recipe cherry clafoutis  In a medium bowl  mix together the flour  sugar  and salt.
In the recipe cherry clafoutis  Add the eggs and stir well to combine.
In the recipe cherry clafoutis  Add the half-and-half and vanilla and whisk until smooth.
In the recipe cherry clafoutis  Melt the butter in an 8-inch (20 cm) cast-iron skillet over medium heat.
In the recipe cherry clafoutis  Once the butter has melted  remove the pan from the heat.
In the recipe cherry clafoutis  Spread the cherries evenly in the pan.
In the recipe cherry clafoutis  Pour the batter over the cherries.
In the recipe cherry clafoutis  Bake for 40-45 minutes  until the clafoutis is golden brown and firm to the touch.
In the recipe cherry clafoutis  Dust the powdered_sugar on top.
In the recipe cherry hand pies  Combine cherries  sugar  cornstarch  almond_extract  and lemon_juice in a saucepan.
In the recipe cherry hand pies  Cook over low heat for 5-10 minutes  crushing the cherries with a spoon and stirring occasionally.
In the recipe cherry hand pies  Roll out the puff pastry.
In the recipe cherry hand pies  Using a cookie cutter  cut 9 rounds out of each sheet of pastry.
In the recipe cherry hand pies  Fill each round with a spoonful of cherry filling.
In the recipe cherry hand pies  Fold in half over the filling and pinch closed with your fingers  followed by a fork.
In the recipe cherry hand pies  Place on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.
In the recipe cherry hand pies  Brush with egg wash and sprinkle with raw_sugar.
In the recipe cherry hand pies  Bake 10-12 minutes until golden brown and puffy.
In the recipe cherry hand pies  Cool slightly and serve with a cup of coffee.
In the recipe cherry moscow mule  In a glass  muddle maraschino_cherries and lime_juice.
In the recipe cherry moscow mule  Add vodka and stir.
In the recipe cherry moscow mule  In a copper mug  pour cherry mixture over ice and top it off with ginger_beer.
In the recipe cherry moscow mule  Add edible flowers for garnish.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Add the sugar and cornstarch to a large saucepan and whisk until combined.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Stir in the water and lemon_juice.

In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Cook over medium heat  whisking until the sugar has dissolved  then reduce the heat to medium-low and simmer until a thick syrup forms and turns golden  about 5 minutes.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Add the cherries and cook for another 2-3 minutes until syrup has thickened.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Turn off the heat and stir in the almond_extract.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Line an 8-inch (20 cm) springform pan with plastic wrap.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Transfer the cherry filling to the pan and spread evenly.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Freeze for 2-3 hours  until firm.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Combine the crushed cookies with the melted butter in a medium bowl until well-combined.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Transfer the cookie crumb mixture to a 10-inch (25 cm) springform pan.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Use a spatula or measuring cup to press the cookie crumbs down to form an even base.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Freeze for 10 minutes.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  In a large bowl  beat the cream_cheese  sugar  and vanilla_extract together with an electric hand mixer until combined.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Add the heavy_cream and beat for another 2-3 minutes until combined and fluffy.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Spread half the cheesecake mixture over the chilled cookie crust.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Freeze for 10 minutes.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Unwrap the cherry pie filling  and place it on top of the set cheesecake layer.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Cover with the remaining cheesecake batter  spreading until smooth on top.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Decorate with fresh berries.
In the recipe cherry pie filled cheesecake  Chill in the fridge for at least 4 hours before slicing and serving.
In the recipe cherry vanilla soda  Add the cherries to a food processor and puree until smooth.
In the recipe cherry vanilla soda  Transfer the cherry puree to a saucepan over medium heat with the simple_syrup and vanilla.
In the recipe cherry vanilla soda  Simmer for 5 minutes  until slightly reduced.
In the recipe cherry vanilla soda  To make the soda  pour 1 cup (240 ml) of seltzer_water into a glass filled with ice and add 1-2 tablespoons of cherry syrup.
In the recipe cheskas family fruitcake  In a small bowl  combine the raisins and sweet red_wine.
In the recipe cheskas family fruitcake  Let sit for at least 10 minutes  until the raisins absorb some of the wine.
In the recipe cheskas family fruitcake  In a medium bowl  use an electric hand mixer to beat the egg whites until medium peaks form.
In the recipe cheskas family fruitcake  In a large bowl  use an electric hand mixer to cream together the butter and sugar.
In the recipe cheskas family fruitcake  Add the egg yolks and beat until incorporated.
In the recipe cheskas family fruitcake  Add the salt to the flour  then gradually add the flour mixture to the wet ingredients  beating until just incorporated.
In the recipe cheskas family fruitcake  Using a rubber spatula  fold in the soaked raisins  walnuts  and glazed fruit until just combined.
In the recipe cheskas family fruitcake  Gently fold in the egg whites.
In the recipe cheskas family fruitcake  Transfer the batter to a 9x5-inch (23x13 cm) loaf pan and smooth the top.
In the recipe cheskas family fruitcake  Bake for 2 hours 15 minutes to 2 hours 30 minutes  until a skewer inserted in the center of the cake comes out clean.
In the recipe cheskas family fruitcake  Serve immediately or wrap in plastic wrap and refrigerate for up to 7 days.
In the recipe chewy granola bars  In a large mixing bowl  combine the oats  rice cereal  coconut_oil  honey  brown_sugar  salt  and vanilla until evenly mixed.
In the recipe chewy granola bars  For chocolate chip  take 1⁄4 of the oats mix and combine with chocolate_chips.
In the recipe chewy granola bars  Stir until mixed.
In the recipe chewy granola bars  Move the mixture to a small baking dish.
In the recipe chewy granola bars  For Apple Cinnamon  take 1⁄4 of the oats mix and combine with dried apples  cinnamon  and nutmeg.
In the recipe chewy granola bars  Stir until mixed.
In the recipe chewy granola bars  Move the mixture to a small baking dish.
In the recipe chewy granola bars  For Cherry Almond  take 1⁄4 of the oats mix and combine with almonds and cherries.
In the recipe chewy granola bars  Stir until mixed.
In the recipe chewy granola bars  Move the mixture to a small baking dish.
In the recipe chewy granola bars  For Peanut Butter Crunch  take 1⁄4 of the oats mix and combine with pretzels  peanut_butter  and chocolate candies.
In the recipe chewy granola bars  Stir until mixed.
In the recipe chewy granola bars  Move the mixture to a small baking dish.
In the recipe chewy granola bars  Enjoy!
In the recipe chewy oatmeal breakfast bars to go  Combine wet ingredients together in a large bowl.
In the recipe chewy oatmeal breakfast bars to go  Then add in all the remaining dry ingredients.
In the recipe chewy oatmeal breakfast bars to go  Add mixture into a 8x8 inch (20x20 cm) baking pan lined with greased parchment paper.
In the recipe chewy oatmeal breakfast bars to go  Firmly press down mixture until it is one smooth layer.
In the recipe chewy oatmeal breakfast bars to go  Bake 15-20 minutes  or until golden brown.
In the recipe chewy oatmeal breakfast bars to go  Let cool 10 minutes.
In the recipe chewy oatmeal breakfast bars to go  Drizzle top with melted dark_chocolate.
In the recipe chewy oatmeal breakfast bars to go  Chill for 30 minutes  or until dark_chocolate is solid.
In the recipe chewy oatmeal breakfast bars to go  Cut into 8 equal pieces.
In the recipe chewy oatmeal breakfast bars to go  Wrap each bar in parchment paper or foil.
In the recipe chewy oatmeal breakfast bars to go  Store in the freezer for up to 3 months or in the refrigerator up to 1 week.
In the recipe chia seed jam  Combine the berries and water in a small saucepan over medium-low heat.
In the recipe chia seed jam  Cook for 15-20 minutes  stirring frequently  until the fruit is broken down and the mixture is saucy.

In the recipe chia seed jam  Remove the pot from the heat and stir in the chia_seeds  lemon_juice  honey (start with a small amount and add more as needed  depending on how sweet the fruit is)  and salt.
In the recipe chia seed jam  Let sit for 10 minutes to allow the chia_seeds to hydrate and thicken the jam.
In the recipe chia seed jam  Then transfer to a resealable jar.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  In a microwave-proof liquid measuring cup  combine the water and the milk.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Microwave on high for 45 seconds.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  In a large bowl  combine the flour  sugar  salt  garlic_powder  Parmesan  and yeast.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Mix thoroughly.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Pour the milk mixture over the dry ingredients.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Stir to combine.

In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Knead the dough on a clean surface for 5 minutes until smooth  if the dough is sticking to the surface add olive_oil 1 teaspoon at a time  then form into a tight ball.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Drizzle 2 tablespoons olive_oil in a large bowl.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Place the dough in the bowl and cover with plastic wrap.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Let rise for 1 hour.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  In a separate large bowl  combine the chicken  2 cups (200 g) mozzarella  Parmesan  garlic_powder  pepper  and alfredo_sauce.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Mix thoroughly.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Place the risen dough onto a floured surface.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Roll out the dough so it is twice as long as it is wide and about 1⁄4 inch (1⁄2 cm) thick.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Transfer the dough to a parchment-lined baking sheet.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Roll up all of the sides of the dough to create an oval shape.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Pinch the dough and pull it while twisting  wrapping the dough into little spirals and placing it onto the rolled edge of the dough.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Pour the chicken alfredo mixture over the dough and spread it until it reaches the edges of the dough.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Brush the sides of the dough with egg wash.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Sprinkle the rest of the mozzarella on top of the chicken alfredo mixture.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Bake for 30 minutes  until the crust is golden brown.
In the recipe chicken alfredo bread boat  Sprinkle with parsley.
In the recipe chicken alfredo dippers  Spread pizza_dough out on a parchment-lined pan.
In the recipe chicken alfredo dippers  Top with alfredo_sauce  mozzarella  chicken  tomato  and parsley.
In the recipe chicken alfredo dippers  Bake an additional 10 minutes.
In the recipe chicken alfredo dippers  Slice and dip!
In the recipe chicken alfredo lasagna  Slice each chicken_breasts in half lengthwise and sprinkle 1 teaspoon of salt  pepper  and garlic_powder evenly on both sides of each chicken_breast.
In the recipe chicken alfredo lasagna  Heat oil in a large pan over high heat  then sear the chicken for about 1 minute per side.
In the recipe chicken alfredo lasagna  In the residual oil (drain some if necessary)  toss in the garlic and onions  stirring constantly until the mixture has started to brown.
In the recipe chicken alfredo lasagna  Pour in the cream  stirring until it starts to boil  then add the parmesan and parsley.
In the recipe chicken alfredo lasagna  Cook for 1 additional minute  then remove from heat.
In the recipe chicken alfredo lasagna  In a 9" x 13" (23cm x 33cm) rectangular baking pan  spread about 1⁄4 of the cream mixture on the bottom.
In the recipe chicken alfredo lasagna  Lay enough lasagna_noodles to cover the sauce  then spread about 1⁄2 of the remaining cream mixture on top.
In the recipe chicken alfredo lasagna  Place enough chicken_breasts to cover the sauce  then sprinkle with half of the mozzarella  followed by half of the bacon and half of the parsley.
In the recipe chicken alfredo lasagna  Repeat the layers once more  starting with noodles  sauce  chicken  bacon  parsley  and mozzarella.
In the recipe chicken alfredo lasagna  Cool for about 15 minutes  slice  and serve!
In the recipe chicken alfredo pizza  Roll out dough to about 10 - 12 inches (25-30 cm) in diameter.
In the recipe chicken alfredo pizza  Top pizza with alfredo_sauce  chicken  and tomatoes.
In the recipe chicken alfredo pizza  Garnish with parsley and cut into 8 slices.
In the recipe chicken alfredo ravioli lasagna  In a large sauté pan  melt the butter over medium heat.
In the recipe chicken alfredo ravioli lasagna  Add the garlic and sauté for 2-3 minutes  until softened.
In the recipe chicken alfredo ravioli lasagna  Add the heavy_cream and Parmesan and stir to incorporate.
In the recipe chicken alfredo ravioli lasagna  Once the mixture comes to a low boil  reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10-15 minutes  until the sauce coats the back of a spoon.
In the recipe chicken alfredo ravioli lasagna  Season with salt  pepper  and nutmeg.
In the recipe chicken alfredo ravioli lasagna  Pour a thin layer of sauce in a the bottom of a 9x13-inch (23x33 cm) glass baking dish.
In the recipe chicken alfredo ravioli lasagna  Arrange 1 package of spinach ricotta ravioli over the sauce.
In the recipe chicken alfredo ravioli lasagna  Top with 1 cup of shredded chicken and 1⁄2 cup (50 g) of mozzarella_cheese.
In the recipe chicken alfredo ravioli lasagna  Cover with more sauce.
In the recipe chicken alfredo ravioli lasagna  Arrange another package of ravioli over the first layer  and top with the remaining cup of shredded chicken and another 1⁄2 cup (50 g) of mozzarella.
In the recipe chicken alfredo ravioli lasagna  Top with more sauce.
In the recipe chicken alfredo ravioli lasagna  Add the last package of ravioli and cover with remaining sauce  making sure all the ravioli are covered.
In the recipe chicken alfredo ravioli lasagna  Top with the remaining cup of shredded mozzarella_cheese.

In the recipe chocolate banana cream sandwiches  Cover with remaining brownie batter.
In the recipe chocolate banana cream sandwiches  Let it cool before slicing out the graham_crackers.
In the recipe chocolate banana cream sandwiches  In a blender  combine the bananas  vanilla  and maple_syrup.
In the recipe chocolate banana cream sandwiches  Blend on high until creamy.
In the recipe chocolate banana cream sandwiches  Use a bag to squeeze the filling onto the crust.
In the recipe chocolate banana cream sandwiches  Top with another crust.
In the recipe chocolate banana cream sandwiches  Enjoy!
In the recipe chocolate banana crepe tower  Scoop a 1⁄4 cup (60 g) of the batter into the pan.
In the recipe chocolate banana crepe tower  Swirl the pan around until the batter evenly coats the bottom.
In the recipe chocolate banana crepe tower  Cook until the surface begins to bubble slightly and the edges brown  about 3 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate banana crepe tower  Remove from the skillet and set aside to cool.
In the recipe chocolate banana crepe tower  Spread the chocolate_hazelnut_spread over the crepes.
In the recipe chocolate banana crepe tower  Roll up.
In the recipe chocolate banana crepe tower  Cut off each end  then cut the each roll in half crosswise.
In the recipe chocolate banana crepe tower  To serve  set 3 rolls on a plate and top with 4 banana slices.
In the recipe chocolate banana crepe tower  Top with 3 more rolls perpendicular to the first stack  more bananas  and one more layer of crepe rolls.
In the recipe chocolate banana crepe tower  Top with whipped_cream.
In the recipe chocolate banana french toast breakfast bake  Make the banana custard: In a large bowl  mash the bananas.
In the recipe chocolate banana french toast breakfast bake  Add the eggs  milk  and heavy_cream and stir to combine.
In the recipe chocolate banana french toast breakfast bake  In a medium bowl  combine the sugar  cinnamon  nutmeg  and vanilla and mix with a fork.
In the recipe chocolate banana french toast breakfast bake  Add the sugar mixture to the custard mixture and stir to combine.
In the recipe chocolate banana french toast breakfast bake  Add the cubed bread  chocolate_chips  and pecans to the custard mixture and toss well to coat.
In the recipe chocolate banana french toast breakfast bake  Let soak for 10 minutes.

In the recipe chocolate banana french toast breakfast bake  While the bread is soaking  make the caramel base: In a medium microwave-safe bowl  microwave the butter for about 2 minutes  stirring every 30 seconds  until melted and hot.
In the recipe chocolate banana french toast breakfast bake  Add the brown_sugar and stir to combine.
In the recipe chocolate banana french toast breakfast bake  Microwave for another minute  stirring halfway  until the sugar is mostly dissolved.
In the recipe chocolate banana french toast breakfast bake  Add the salt  vanilla  and pecans and stir to combine.
In the recipe chocolate banana french toast breakfast bake  Pour the caramel into the bottom of a 9 (22 cm) x 13-inch (33 cm) baking dish and spread evenly.
In the recipe chocolate banana french toast breakfast bake  Arrange the bananas  cut side down  over the caramel.
In the recipe chocolate banana french toast breakfast bake  Spoon the brioche-custard mixture evenly over the bananas.
In the recipe chocolate banana french toast breakfast bake  Cover with foil and bake for 30 minutes  then uncover and bake for 40-45 minutes longer  until the custard is set.
In the recipe chocolate banana french toast breakfast bake  Remove from the oven and let cool for 5 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate banana french toast breakfast bake  Run a knife around the edges of the baking dish to loosen the bake  then invert onto a rectangular serving dish.
In the recipe chocolate banana french toast breakfast bake  Slice and serve.
In the recipe chocolate banana mug cake  Mash banana into a paste then add chocolate_chips.
In the recipe chocolate banana mug cake  Whisk together egg  oil  honey  milk  and vanilla extract in a small bowl.
In the recipe chocolate banana mug cake  Whisk together flour  cocoa_powder  baking_powder  and salt in a small bowl.
In the recipe chocolate banana mug cake  Pour the wet ingredients into the dry ingredients and mix until combined.
In the recipe chocolate banana mug cake  Grease 2 small mugs.
In the recipe chocolate banana mug cake  Fill mugs half way with the chocolate batter.
In the recipe chocolate banana mug cake  Divide the banana filling between the 2 mugs.
In the recipe chocolate banana mug cake  Place remaining chocolate batter on top.
In the recipe chocolate banana mug cake  Garnish with sliced banana.
In the recipe chocolate banana pecan lace cup  Scoop about 2 tablespoons of banana pudding into the pecan lace cookie cup.
In the recipe chocolate banana pecan lace cup  Place 3 slices of banana over the pudding.
In the recipe chocolate banana pecan lace cup  Drizzle the leftover melted chocolate over the bananas.
In the recipe chocolate banoffee biscuit balls  Crush Digestive Biscuits in a large plastic bag.
In the recipe chocolate banoffee biscuit balls  Pour into a large bowl and add Banana and about half the can of Dulce De Leche.
In the recipe chocolate banoffee biscuit balls  Use a fork to mash and incorporate the banana and toffee into the biscuit crumbs.
In the recipe chocolate banoffee biscuit balls  Form the mixture into 1 inch (2 1⁄2 cm) balls and freeze for 15 minutes until firm.
In the recipe chocolate banoffee biscuit balls  Remove balls from freezer and dip into the melted chocolate.
In the recipe chocolate banoffee biscuit balls  Set on wax paper and sprinkle with additional biscuit crumbs (optional).
In the recipe chocolate banoffee biscuit balls  Allow chocolate coating to harden (chill in fridge to speed up this process).
In the recipe chocolate banoffee biscuit balls  Drizzle with additional toffee just before serving.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Make the ladyfingers: In a large bowl  beat the egg whites and cream_of_tartar with an electric hand mixer until foamy.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Gradually add 1⁄4 cup sugar while continuing to beat until stiff peaks form.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  In a medium bowl  beat together the egg yolks and remaining 1⁄2 cup sugar until thick and pale in color  about 3 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Gently fold the yolks into egg white mixture with a rubber spatula.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Sift in the flour and salt and fold to incorporate.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Transfer the batter to a piping bag or zip-top bag fitted with a large round tip.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Release the bottom from a 9-inch springform pan and set the ring in the center of a prepared baking sheet.

In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Starting at the center of the ring and working your way outward  pipe the batter in a spiral pattern  about 1 centimeter thick  leaving a 1⁄2-inch border around the edge.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Remove the ring.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  With the remaining batter  pipe 40 3-inch (10-centimeter) long by 1-inch (21⁄2-centimeter) wide cookies onto the remaining 2 prepared baking sheet.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Bake the spiral and cookies for 15-17 minutes  until lightly golden around the edges.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Make the chocolate mousse: In a large bowl  beat the cold heavy_cream with an electric hand mixer until soft peaks form.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Add the sugar and beat to incorporate.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  In a medium bowl  pour the hot heavy_cream over the chocolate.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Stir with a rubber spatula until melted and smooth.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Fold the chocolate mixture into the whipped cream until incorporated.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Set the spiral cake base on the bottom of the springform pan and attach the ring.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Line the gap on the inside edge of the ring with the ladyfingers  flat sides facing in.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Pour the chocolate mousse into the center and smooth in an even layer.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Chill until set  at least 4 hours in the refrigerator or about 2 hours in the freezer.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Garnish the charlotte with blackberries  raspberries  chocolate shavings  and mint_sprigs.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Release the springform and tie a ribbon around the outside of the charlotte.
In the recipe chocolate berry charlotte  Remove the ribbon before slicing and serving.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Combine the yeast and warm milk and let sit until foamy  about 5 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  In large mixing bowl  add the egg  egg_yolks  vanilla  sugar  and honey and whisk to combine.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Add in the milk and yeast mixture and whisk until fully incorporated.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Gradually add in the flour and mix until fully incorporated.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Gradually add in the butter and mix until fully incorporated.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Bring out the dough onto floured work surface and knead until smooth.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Divide the dough into two equal parts and place in bowls and cover each with plastic wrap.

In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  For the chocolate sauce  combine bittersweet_chocolate  butter  sugar  cocoa_powder  cinnamon  espresso_powder  and turbinado_sugar in a medium sized mixing bowl and microwave for 1-2 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Stir to combine and set aside.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Once the dough has doubled in size  transfer to a floured work surface and roll both pieces of dough into a rectangle roughly 10x15-inches.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Cover the dough with half of the chocolate sauce leaving an 1⁄2 inch - 1 inch of room on all sides.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Gently roll the dough up and repeat with second piece of dough and remaining chocolate sauce.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Using a bench scraper or a knife  carefully cut each log vertically in half making sure the seam is side down.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Lay one piece of dough horizontally and lay another piece over it vertically so you have a rough ‘plus sign’.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Lay another piece horizontally over the vertical piece and above the other horizontal piece.

In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Lay the final piece vertically on the right of the other vertical piece having it go over the top horizontal piece but weaving it under the lower horizontal piece.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Starting with the bottom vertical piece on the right side  bring it to the left layering it over the other vertical lower piece.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Take the original piece you crossed over (the lower left vertical piece) and cross that over to the right layering it over the last piece you used.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Tuck in the excess pieces of dough under the bread.
In the recipe chocolate braided swirl bread babka  Transfer the bread into a parchment paper-lined baking sheet and brush with egg_wash.
In the recipe chocolate brownie dip  Add chickpeas  maple_syrup  milk of choice  vanilla  and cocoa powder to a food processor and blend until smooth.
In the recipe chocolate brownie dip  Top with shredded_coconut and serve with your favorite fruit or dipping snack.
In the recipe chocolate caramel pretzel pinwheels  Combine cereal and crushed pretzels in a large bowl.
In the recipe chocolate caramel pretzel pinwheels  In another large bowl  melt marshmallows and butter in the microwave for 1 minute & 30 seconds  stirring half way.
In the recipe chocolate caramel pretzel pinwheels  Combine cereal  pretzels and melted marshmallows.
In the recipe chocolate caramel pretzel pinwheels  Mix well.
In the recipe chocolate caramel pretzel pinwheels  Prepare a baking sheet with parchment paper and spray generously with non-stick cooking spray.
In the recipe chocolate caramel pretzel pinwheels  Remove marshmallow mixture from the bowl and place onto the baking sheet.
In the recipe chocolate caramel pretzel pinwheels  Spray another piece of parchment paper with non-stick spray and lay the sprayed side on top of the marshmallow mixture.
In the recipe chocolate caramel pretzel pinwheels  Roll out with a rolling pin into a thin layer.
In the recipe chocolate caramel pretzel pinwheels  Remove the top layer of parchment paper and evenly spread caramel over the marshmallow mixture.
In the recipe chocolate caramel pretzel pinwheels  Pour chocolate_chips over the caramel.
In the recipe chocolate caramel pretzel pinwheels  Bake for 2 minutes  or until chocolate_chips spread easily across the caramel.
In the recipe chocolate caramel pretzel pinwheels  Carefully & tightly roll it up longways  peeling back the parchment paper as you go.
In the recipe chocolate caramel pretzel pinwheels  Cover in plastic wrap & chill for 2-3 hours  or until it has firmed up nicely.
In the recipe chocolate caramel pretzel pinwheels  Remove plastic wrap and parchment paper  and cut in 1-inch (2 cm) slices.
In the recipe chocolate chantilly 2 ingredient chocolate mousse  Melt chocolate and water together in a pan on a low heat  stirring occasionally until melted.
In the recipe chocolate chantilly 2 ingredient chocolate mousse  Add ice and water to a large bowl  then place the mixing bowl in the ice water.
In the recipe chocolate chantilly 2 ingredient chocolate mousse  Pour the melted chocolate mixture into the mixing bowl in the ice bath.
In the recipe chocolate chantilly 2 ingredient chocolate mousse  Using a hand blender  whisk chocolate mixture until it becomes fluffy and resembles whipped_cream  do not over mix!
In the recipe chocolate chantilly 2 ingredient chocolate mousse  Top with whipped_cream and grated chocolate.
In the recipe chocolate chantilly 2 ingredient chocolate mousse  Enjoy!
In the recipe chocolate cheesecake pudding cups  Open the chocolate_pudding cups and spoon the pudding into a medium bowl.
In the recipe chocolate cheesecake pudding cups  Place the pudding in the refrigerator and wash out the plastic cups.
In the recipe chocolate cheesecake pudding cups  Using scissors  cut the cups down one side and across the bottom  leaving one side of the cup intact.
In the recipe chocolate cheesecake pudding cups  Tape the cut edges together to seal the cups.
In the recipe chocolate cheesecake pudding cups  Set aside.
In the recipe chocolate cheesecake pudding cups  Place the chocolate chips in a medium microwave-safe bowl.
In the recipe chocolate cheesecake pudding cups  Add the coconut_oil and melt in the microwave in 30-second intervals for 1 minute total.
In the recipe chocolate cheesecake pudding cups  Stir the chocolate until smooth.
In the recipe chocolate cheesecake pudding cups  Spoon the melted chocolate into the plastic cups.
In the recipe chocolate cheesecake pudding cups  Tilt the cups to coat the insides completely and pour any excess chocolate back into the bowl.
In the recipe chocolate cheesecake pudding cups  Place the cups on a baking sheet and refrigerate until set  about 5 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate cheesecake pudding cups  Add the cream_cheese to a medium bowl with the sugar and vanilla.
In the recipe chocolate cheesecake pudding cups  Stir until smooth and well-combined.
In the recipe chocolate cheesecake pudding cups  Peel the tape off the pudding cups and carefully remove the plastic from the chocolate cups.
In the recipe chocolate cheesecake pudding cups  Flip the cups upright and pipe the chocolate_pudding into the bottom of the cups.

In the recipe chocolate cheesecake pudding cups  Top the pudding with the cheesecake mixture and your favorite dessert toppings  such as crushed peanuts  caramel sauce  crushed cookies  and/or strawberries.
In the recipe chocolate cherry skillet cobbler  In a cast-iron skillet over medium-low heat  add the cherries  sugar  cornstarch  lemon_juice  and salt.
In the recipe chocolate cherry skillet cobbler  Mix to combine and stir for 5-10 minutes until the mixture starts to thicken.
In the recipe chocolate cherry skillet cobbler  Sprinkle the box cake mix over the cherry filling.
In the recipe chocolate cherry skillet cobbler  Distribute the butter evenly over the top to ensure even baking.
In the recipe chocolate cherry skillet cobbler  Bake for 45 minutes to an hour  until the top is golden brown.
In the recipe chocolate cherry skillet cobbler  Serve warm with ice cream.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana box bread  In a large bowl  mash the bananas.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana box bread  Add the eggs and vegetable_oil and whisk until smooth.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana box bread  Add the cake_mix and chocolate_chips and stir with a spatula to combine.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana box bread  Split and pour the batter into two loaf pans lined with parchment paper and nonstick baking spray.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana box bread  Bake for 30 minutes or until toothpick comes out clean when inserted in the middle.

In the recipe chocolate chip banana bread overnight oats  Stir together.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana bread overnight oats  Seal and place in the refrigerator overnight for up to five days.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana monkey bread  Cut one banana into coins and line the bottom of a greased bundt pan.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana monkey bread  Cut each biscuit round in half and flatten into rounds.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana monkey bread  Stuff each round with one piece of the halved banana coins and chocolate chips.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana monkey bread  Close the round together by pinching at the seam and roll into a ball in your hands.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana monkey bread  Place the balls in the cinnamon sugar mix and gently toss to coat.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana monkey bread  Place half the balls in the pan.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana monkey bread  In a saucepan over medium heat melt the butter and brown_sugar until one  stirring occasionally.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana monkey bread  Pour half of the glaze on top.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana monkey bread  Sprinkle a handful of chocolate chips over top.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana monkey bread  Then place rest of the balls on top followed by the rest of the glaze.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana monkey bread  Remove from oven and allow it to cool or about 15-30 minutes before turning it over onto a plate.
In the recipe chocolate chip banana monkey bread  Enjoy!
In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  In a large mixing bowl  use a fork to mash the ripe bananas.
In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  Whisk in the egg  followed by vegetable_oil and milk.
In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  Mix until combined.
In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  Add in the yellow_cake_mix  being careful to not overmix.
In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  Use a rubber spatula to gently fold in the chocolate_chips.

In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  In a shallow saucepan  set over medium heat  add the butter and brown sugar  and stir constantly with a wooden spoon until the mixture turns into golden brown syrup  about 5 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  Pour the syrup into a 9-inch (20-cm) round cake pan.
In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  Place the sliced bananas into a single layer on top of the syrup.
In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  Divide the cake batter among the banana pan  and another greased 9-inch (20-cm) cake pan.
In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  Bake for 20-25 minutes  or until a toothpick comes out clean from the center.

In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  Beat in the eggs  one at a time.
In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  Add in the sour_cream and vanilla_extract  and mix until combined.
In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  Pour the cheesecake batter into the cooled cake in the pan.
In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  Cover the bottom of the pan with two sheets of foil and place into a larger baking dish.
In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  Fill the baking dish with water until it comes 1 inch (2 cm) up the side on the cake pan.
In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  Bake for 1 hour.
In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  To assemble  remove the cheesecake from the springform pan.
In the recipe chocolate chip bananas foster box cheesecake  Top the cake with the cooled banana fosters cake.
In the recipe chocolate chip brownie cheesecake  Prepare the brownie_mix according to package instructions  and pour the batter into a springform pan.

In the recipe chocolate chip brownie cheesecake  Fold in vanilla and whipped cream  then fold in the chocolate_chips.
In the recipe chocolate chip brownie cheesecake  Spread cream_cheese mixture over the cooled brownie in the springform pan.
In the recipe chocolate chip brownie cheesecake  Enjoy!
In the recipe chocolate chip cake mix cookies  Combine cake mix  chocolate_chips  oil  and eggs in a mixing bowl.
In the recipe chocolate chip cake mix cookies  Using an ice cream scoop or your hand  form golf ball-sized balls of cookie dough and transfer to a parchment paper-lined baking sheet.
In the recipe chocolate chip cake mix cookies  Bake at 350°F (180°C) for 10-12 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate chip chickpea cookie dough  Add chocolate_chips to dough.
In the recipe chocolate chip chickpea cookie dough  Mix well.
In the recipe chocolate chip chickpea cookie dough  Serve and enjoy!
In the recipe chocolate chip cookies  In a large bowl  whisk together the brown_sugar  granulated_sugar  and melted butter  until evenly combined and light in color.
In the recipe chocolate chip cookies  Add in the eggs and vanilla  mixing until smooth.
In the recipe chocolate chip cookies  Add the flour and baking soda  folding the mixture until it forms a smooth dough.
In the recipe chocolate chip cookies  Fold in the chocolate_chips until evenly combined.
In the recipe chocolate chip cookies  Using an ice cream scoop  scoop 6 balls of dough onto a baking tray lined with parchment paper.
In the recipe chocolate chip cookies  Bake for 12 minutes  then serve!
In the recipe chocolate chip cookies  To save cookie dough for later use  scoop the dough into balls and place them side-by-side on a baking tray lined with parchment paper.
In the recipe chocolate chip cookies  Wrap the tray with cling wrap  then freeze for up to one month.
In the recipe chocolate chip edible cookie dough  Soak cashews in boiling water for two hours.
In the recipe chocolate chip edible cookie dough  Drain the cashews and blend in a food processor for 30 seconds.
In the recipe chocolate chip edible cookie dough  Pour in coconut_oil and agave and blend for 1 minute.
In the recipe chocolate chip edible cookie dough  Scrape down sides and add in almond_flour.
In the recipe chocolate chip edible cookie dough  Blend until smooth  approximately 2-5 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate chip edible cookie dough  Remove the mixture from the food processor and transfer to a food storage container and stir in chocolate_chips.
In the recipe chocolate chip edible cookie dough  Store in an airtight container in the refrigerator.
In the recipe chocolate chip granola bites  Mix together oats  cinnamon  vanilla_extract  nut_butter  honey  and chocolate_chips in a medium bowl until well-incorporated.
In the recipe chocolate chip granola bites  Cover with plastic wrap and chill in the refrigerator for an hour.
In the recipe chocolate chip granola bites  Roll into balls the size of a ping pong ball.
In the recipe chocolate chip granola bites  Refrigerate in tightly sealed container for up to one week.
In the recipe chocolate chip lava cookies  In a large bowl  combine the butter  vanilla  canola_oil  sugar  and salt and beat with a hand mixer until smooth.
In the recipe chocolate chip lava cookies  Add the egg and mix until well incorporated.
In the recipe chocolate chip lava cookies  Add the cornstarch  flour  and chocolate_chips.
In the recipe chocolate chip lava cookies  Using a spatula  mix well until fully combined.
In the recipe chocolate chip lava cookies  Cover the dough with plastic and chill in the fridge at least 30 minutes to overnight
In the recipe chocolate chip lava cookies  Divide the cookie dough into 12 portions.
In the recipe chocolate chip lava cookies  Take one and line the base and sides of a cup.
In the recipe chocolate chip lava cookies  Repeat with the remaining cups.
In the recipe chocolate chip lava cookies  Fill each cookie cup with a chocolate truffle.
In the recipe chocolate chip lava cookies  Place the circle over the top of the filling  and press down the edges to make sure it seals to the other dough.
In the recipe chocolate chip lava cookies  Enjoy!
In the recipe chocolate chip muffin mug  Mix together egg_white  honey  and vanilla_extract in a greased coffee mug.
In the recipe chocolate chip muffin mug  Add oat_flour and baking_powder and mix until combined.
In the recipe chocolate chip muffin mug  Add in chocolate_chips.

In the recipe chocolate chip peanut bars  Serve immediately or store in an airtight container in the refrigerator for up to 1 week.

In the recipe chocolate chip skillet cookie  Place the chocolate chunks in the middle of the cookie_dough  then place the other flattened 1⁄3 of the cookie_dough on top.
In the recipe chocolate chip skillet cookie  Crimp the edges of the dough together to seal in the chocolate.
In the recipe chocolate chip skillet cookie  Bake for 35-40 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate chip skillet cookie  Serve warm with ice_cream and caramel_sauce.

In the recipe chocolate coconut almond balls  Roll the mixture into 1-inch (2.5 cm) balls and place on a wax paper lined baking sheet.
In the recipe chocolate coconut almond balls  Freeze for 15 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate coconut almond balls  Break apart chocolate bars and add to a microwave safe bowl.
In the recipe chocolate coconut almond balls  Microwave chocolate for 75 seconds  stopping every 30 seconds to check and stir.
In the recipe chocolate coconut almond balls  Remove the coconut balls from the freezer and individually roll in melted chocolate to coat.
In the recipe chocolate coconut almond balls  Place back on a wax paper lined tray and sprinkle with additional coconut and top with an almond (optional).
In the recipe chocolate coconut cream bars  Combine shredded_coconut  coconut_cream  maple_syrup  and a pinch of salt to a food processor and blend until mixture becomes easily moldable.
In the recipe chocolate coconut cream bars  You may have to press down the mixture and reblend a few times for this to happen.
In the recipe chocolate coconut cream bars  Pour mixture into an 8x8-inch (20x20-cm) pan lined with parchment or wax paper.
In the recipe chocolate coconut cream bars  Press down firmly with a rubber spatula and smooth mixture into an even layer.
In the recipe chocolate coconut cream bars  Freeze for 30 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate coconut cream bars  Prepare chocolate layer by combining dark chocolate_chips and coconut_cream in a bowl.
In the recipe chocolate coconut cream bars  Microwave in 15-second intervals  stirring mixture thoroughly in between.
In the recipe chocolate coconut cream bars  Pour chocolate mixture on top of the coconut_cream layer and spread into an even layer with a rubber spatula.
In the recipe chocolate coconut cream bars  Sprinkle shredded_coconut on top.
In the recipe chocolate coconut cream bars  Freeze for 1 hour  or until chocolate layer has set.
In the recipe chocolate coconut cream bars  Cut into 16 squares.
In the recipe chocolate coconut frozen bananas  Dip the bananas into the chocolate coating.
In the recipe chocolate coconut frozen bananas  Roll or sprinkle on toppings.
In the recipe chocolate coconut frozen bananas  Place bananas in freezer until the coating has hardened.
In the recipe chocolate coconut frozen bananas  Enjoy!

In the recipe chocolate coconut sheet cake  In a medium bowl  sift together the flour  cinnamon  salt  baking_soda  and cocoa_powder.
In the recipe chocolate coconut sheet cake  Whisk to combine.
In the recipe chocolate coconut sheet cake  In a large bowl  cream together the butter and brown sugar with an electric hand mixer until fluffy.
In the recipe chocolate coconut sheet cake  Add the eggs  1 at a time  beating to incorporate each addition before adding the next.
In the recipe chocolate coconut sheet cake  Add the vanilla and beat to combine.
In the recipe chocolate coconut sheet cake  Add 1⁄2 of the flour mixture to the butter mixture and beat on low speed to incorporate.
In the recipe chocolate coconut sheet cake  Add 1⁄2 of the coconut_milk and beat again.

In the recipe chocolate coconut sheet cake  Bake for 20–25 minutes  or until the center is set and edges begin to pull away from the pan.

In the recipe chocolate coconut sheet cake  Sprinkle the shredded_coconut on top.
In the recipe chocolate coconut sheet cake  Slice and serve.
In the recipe chocolate coconut winter smoothie  In a blender  combine the banana  oats  peanut_butter  cocoa powder  shredded_coconut  maple_syrup  vanilla  and milk.
