In the recipe chocolate coconut winter smoothie  Transfer the chocolate coconut mixture to a small saucepan and heat over medium-low heat until just warmed through.
In the recipe chocolate coconut winter smoothie  Pour into a mug and serve immediately.
In the recipe chocolate cookie cheesecake stuffed brownies  Combine the melted butter and 3 cups (600 g) of sugar in a large bowl and whisk to combine.

In the recipe chocolate cookie cheesecake stuffed brownies  Let sit for a minute to cool before adding the eggs  to avoid cooking them  then add 6 eggs and 2 tablespoons of vanilla and whisk to combine.
In the recipe chocolate cookie cheesecake stuffed brownies  Sift in the flour  cocoa_powder  baking_soda  baking_powder  and salt.
In the recipe chocolate cookie cheesecake stuffed brownies  Whisk until just combined.
In the recipe chocolate cookie cheesecake stuffed brownies  Use a spatula to fold in the chocolate_chips.
In the recipe chocolate cookie cheesecake stuffed brownies  Pour the batter onto the prepared baking sheet  spreading to the edges with a spatula.
In the recipe chocolate cookie cheesecake stuffed brownies  Bake for 25 minutes  or until brownies appear be nearly fully cooked.

In the recipe chocolate cookie cheesecake stuffed brownies  While the brownies are beginning to bake  beat together the cream_cheese and the remaining sugar in a medium bowl with an electric hand mixer until there are no lumps.
In the recipe chocolate cookie cheesecake stuffed brownies  Add the remaining egg and remaining teaspoon of vanilla  beating until evenly combined.

In the recipe chocolate cookie cheesecake stuffed brownies  After 25 minutes  remove the brownies from the oven and use the bottom of a 1⁄4-cup (60 ml) measuring cup to make 24 evenly spaced indentations in the brownies.
In the recipe chocolate cookie cheesecake stuffed brownies  Carefully fill the indentations with cheesecake filling.
In the recipe chocolate cookie cheesecake stuffed brownies  Top each with a chocolate sandwich cookie.
In the recipe chocolate cookie cheesecake stuffed brownies  Return to the oven for 15 more minutes  until the cheesecake filling is set.
In the recipe chocolate cookie cheesecake stuffed brownies  Let cool  then cut into squares and serve.
In the recipe chocolate cookie crust peanut butter pie  Add crushed cookies into a bowl and mix with melted butter.
In the recipe chocolate cookie crust peanut butter pie  Pour crumbs into pie dish and pat down to form a crust.
In the recipe chocolate cookie crust peanut butter pie  In a bowl mix the cream_cheese and peanut_butter until smooth.
In the recipe chocolate cookie crust peanut butter pie  Add in the whipped_cream and powdered_sugar  mix again until smooth.
In the recipe chocolate cookie crust peanut butter pie  Pour mixture over crust and smooth out the top.
In the recipe chocolate cookie crust peanut butter pie  Sprinkle the top with remaining cookie crumbs.
In the recipe chocolate cookie crust peanut butter pie  Slice and serve.
In the recipe chocolate cookie crust peanut butter pie  Enjoy!
In the recipe chocolate covered cheesecake bites  In a plastic bag  crush the graham_crackers finely with the back of a large pot or pan.

In the recipe chocolate covered cheesecake bites  In a large bowl  combine graham_crackers  1⁄4 cup (40g) confectioners’ sugar  salt  and melted butter  stirring until the mixture is the texture of wet sand.
In the recipe chocolate covered cheesecake bites  Dump the graham_cracker mixture into a 9×9 inch (23 x 23 cm) baking dish lined with parchment paper.
In the recipe chocolate covered cheesecake bites  Press the mixture down with your hands to create an even layer.
In the recipe chocolate covered cheesecake bites  In a separate bowl  combine cream_cheese  1 cup (160g) confectioner’s sugar  and vanilla  stirring until smooth.
In the recipe chocolate covered cheesecake bites  Spread the cream_cheese mixture evenly on top of the graham_cracker crust.
In the recipe chocolate covered cheesecake bites  Transfer the frozen cheesecake onto a cutting board  peeling away the parchment paper.
In the recipe chocolate covered cheesecake bites  Slice 1-centimeter-wide (1⁄64 in) strips horizontally  then vertically  creating little cheesecake cubes.
In the recipe chocolate covered cheesecake bites  Dip the cheesecake cubes in the chocolate  dripping off excess  and set them on a tray lined with parchment paper.
In the recipe chocolate covered cheesecake bites  Enjoy!
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberries 4 ways  To make Striped Strawberries  melt 1 tablespoon of coconut_oil with chocolate chips  repeat with the white_chocolate chips.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberries 4 ways  Insert toothpick into the top of a strawberry.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberries 4 ways  Coat strawberry entirely in chocolate  alternating between white and dark.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberries 4 ways  Chill strawberries for about 15 minutes or until hardened.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberries 4 ways  For white_chocolate strawberries drizzle dark chocolate over the top in a quick back and forth motion.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberries 4 ways  For dark chocolate strawberries  do the same with white_chocolate drizzle.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberries 4 ways  Chill once more for 15 minutes or until hardened.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberries 4 ways  Coat strawberry entirely in chocolate  alternating between white and dark.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberries 4 ways  Dip strawberry  while the chocolate is still warm  into a bowl of nuts.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberries 4 ways  Chill once more for 15 minutes or until hardened.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberries 4 ways  Dip strawberry  while the chocolate is still warm  into a bowl of cookie crumbs.

In the recipe chocolate covered strawberries 4 ways  To form the tuxedo  dip one side of the white_chocolate coated strawberry into dark chocolate at an angle  going to the top of white_chocolate coating.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberries 4 ways  Repeat on the other side  leaving a white “V” in the center of the strawberry.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberries 4 ways  With a toothpick  draw a bowtie and buttons with remaining melted dark chocolate.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberry box cupcakes  In a large bowl  prepare the cake batter.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberry box cupcakes  Divide the batter evenly among a lined muffin tin  filling halfway.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberry box cupcakes  Finely chop 8 of the strawberries.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberry box cupcakes  Top with remaining batter  filling about 3⁄4 of the way up.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberry box cupcakes  Bake for 20 minutes  then cool.
In the recipe chocolate covered strawberry box cupcakes  Pipe the frosting onto each cupcake  then top with a chocolate-covered strawberry.
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese croissant bake  Open 2 prepackaged mini croissant rolls and chop them into 2 cm (1 inch) balls.
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese croissant bake  Spray a medium-large baking pan with cooking spray and place the balls in the pan.
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese croissant bake  Sprinkle the chocolate_chips evenly over the dough.
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese croissant bake  In a large bowl  whisk cream_cheese until smooth and creamy  then add the sugar  eggs  and vanilla and whisk together until smooth.
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese croissant bake  Slowly the add milk to loosen the mixture without curdling the cream_cheese.
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese croissant bake  Pour the cream_cheese mixture evenly over the dough  then let sit for 20 minutes (optional).
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese croissant bake  Bake for 45-50 minutes  or until the middle is cooked through.
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese croissant bake  Garnish with a nice scoop of vanilla ice cream.
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese stuffed monkey bread  Cut biscuits in half and cube the cream_cheese (32 pieces).
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese stuffed monkey bread  Flatten each biscuit and place one cube of cream_cheese and a few chocolate_chips in the center of each.
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese stuffed monkey bread  Fold the biscuit_dough around the cream_cheese and chocolate and form into a ball.
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese stuffed monkey bread  In a large plastic bag combine white_sugar and cinnamon.
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese stuffed monkey bread  Add 6-8 dough balls to the bag  seal the bag  and shake until well coated.
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese stuffed monkey bread  In a microwave safe bowl add brown_sugar and butter.
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese stuffed monkey bread  Microwave on high for 70 seconds - stopping halfway to stir.
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese stuffed monkey bread  Remove from microwave and stir until it reaches a caramel consistency.
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese stuffed monkey bread  In a greased bundt pan  sprinkle half of the walnuts  half the dough pieces  and drizzle half the caramel glaze.
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese stuffed monkey bread  Repeat with remaining walnuts  dough  and glaze.
In the recipe chocolate cream cheese stuffed monkey bread  Bake for 30-35 minutes.

In the recipe chocolate cream cheese stuffed monkey bread  Remove from oven and turn upside down onto a plate to cool for 10 minutes before lifting off the pan (this way the warm glaze runs back through and fully coats all the bread)
In the recipe chocolate crunch bark  Place crackers on a greased  parchment paper-lined baking sheet so that the entire surface is covered.
In the recipe chocolate crunch bark  In a saucepan  melt butter on low heat.
In the recipe chocolate crunch bark  Once melted  add brown sugar and turn heat to medium.
In the recipe chocolate crunch bark  Continue stirring until boiling  then boil for 3 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate crunch bark  Pour the caramel over the crackers  spreading evenly with a spatula.
In the recipe chocolate crunch bark  Bake for 5 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate crunch bark  Pour the chocolate_chips over the crackers and cover with tin foil for 3 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate crunch bark  Remove the foil and spread the softened chocolate over the top evenly.
In the recipe chocolate crunch bark  Sprinkle with pecans  cover with foil  and freeze for 1 hour.
In the recipe chocolate crunch bark  Break the bark up into pieces.
In the recipe chocolate dipped cannoli cupcakes  Prepare cake_mix according to its directions.
In the recipe chocolate dipped cannoli cupcakes  Fill liners about 3⁄4 of the way up with the cupcake batter.
In the recipe chocolate dipped cannoli cupcakes  Bake for about 20-25 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate dipped cannoli cupcakes  In a large bowl  combine the ricotta  mascarpone  powdered_sugar  and vanilla.
In the recipe chocolate dipped cannoli cupcakes  Mix until well combined.
In the recipe chocolate dipped cannoli cupcakes  Fold in the mini_chocolate_chips.
In the recipe chocolate dipped cannoli cupcakes  Cut a 1⁄2 inch (1.5cm) hole on the tip of a pastry or zip top bag and fill with the cannoli cream.
In the recipe chocolate dipped cannoli cupcakes  Cut a circle in the center of each cupcake and press the center down into the bottom  creating a hole.
In the recipe chocolate dipped cannoli cupcakes  Fill the cupcake with cannoli cream and use a spiraling motion to create a swirl of the cream on top of the cupcake.
In the recipe chocolate dipped cannoli cupcakes  Put the cupcakes in the freezer for about 1 hour or until firm.
In the recipe chocolate dipped cannoli cupcakes  Melt the dark_chocolate and coconut_oil together.
In the recipe chocolate dipped cannoli cupcakes  Carefully  dip the tops of the cupcakes into the melted chocolate.
In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  Make the taco shells: in a medium bowl  whisk together the eggs and sugar until combined.
In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  Add the milk  vanilla  and butter  and whisk until fully incorporated.
In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  Sift in the flour and cocoa_powder.
In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  Whisk until smooth.
In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  Heat a small non-stick pan over medium-low heat  then add 1⁄3 cup (95 g) of batter at a time and tilt the pan to spread the batter evenly like a crepe.
In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  Cook until bubbles appear on the surface and the batter is set  about 6-8 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  Flip the taco shell and cook on other side for another 3-4 minutes  until cooked through.
In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  If desired  remove the taco shell from pan and place on a grated cooling rack while still hot.
In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  Place a sheet of parchment over the shell and press into the rack  allowing the grate marks to set into the shell.
In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  Rotate the shell 90 degrees and press the cone into the grates again for a waffled look.
In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  Place the taco shells between the cups of an inverted muffin tin to form their shape.
In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  Let set for about 10 minutes  then freeze for 20 minutes to harden.

In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  Make the magic shell: combine the chocolate and coconut_oil in a medium bowl and microwave for 2 minutes  stirring every 30 seconds until melted and shiny.
In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  Remove the taco shells from the freezer and use a spoon to coat the inside of each taco shell with melted magic shell.
In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  Return to the freezer for 20 minutes  until the magic shell hardens.
In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  Remove the shells from the freezer and pipe in the ice cream  filling the tacos.
In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  Freeze for 2 hours.
In the recipe chocolate dipped ice cream tacos  Remove the tacos from the freezer and dip the tops of each taco in the magic shell  then immediately sprinkle with the crushed peanuts.
In the recipe chocolate dipped oranges  Peel orange into slices and insert lollipop_sticks.
In the recipe chocolate dipped oranges  Melt chocolate_chips in microwave at 30-second intervals until the chocolate is easy to stir.
In the recipe chocolate dipped oranges  Dip orange slices halfway in chocolate  and then in each topping of your choice.
In the recipe chocolate dulce de leche ice cream  In a large bowl  whip the cream until soft peaks form.
In the recipe chocolate dulce de leche ice cream  Add the condensed milk and cocoa_powder  then whip until smooth.
In the recipe chocolate dulce de leche ice cream  Drizzle the dulce_de_leche on top.
In the recipe chocolate dulce de leche ice cream  Carefully swirl in the dulce_de_leche  making sure it is not blended into the cream.
In the recipe chocolate dulce de leche ice cream  Serve with more dulce_de_leche.
In the recipe chocolate espresso souffles  In a large bowl  stir together the melted butter and melted chocolate until fully combined and smooth.
In the recipe chocolate espresso souffles  Stir in the espresso_powder  followed by the water.
In the recipe chocolate espresso souffles  Stir in the egg_yolk.
In the recipe chocolate espresso souffles  Add in icing_sugar.
In the recipe chocolate espresso souffles  Stir until combined and smooth.
In the recipe chocolate espresso souffles  In a separate bowl  whisk the egg_white until soft peaks form.
In the recipe chocolate espresso souffles  Gradually add the caster_sugar and whisk until stiff peaks form and they become glossy.
In the recipe chocolate espresso souffles  Fold 2 tablespoons of the whipped egg_whites into the chocolate mixture and fold until fully incorporated.
In the recipe chocolate espresso souffles  Gradually fold in the remaining whipped egg_whites.
In the recipe chocolate espresso souffles  Quickly pour the mixture into the prepared espresso cups or ramekins.
In the recipe chocolate espresso souffles  Using a knife  carefully pull across the top of each soufflé so that the top is completely flat.
In the recipe chocolate espresso souffles  Chill the soufflés in the fridge for 30 minutes (optional) and then preheat the oven to 200°C (400°F).
In the recipe chocolate espresso souffles  Bake for 15 minutes.
In the recipe chocolate espresso souffles  Dust with a little cocoa_powder and serve immediately.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  If your bananas aren’t already very ripe  place them on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  Bake for 15-20 minutes  until they are nearly black.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  Peel the bananas  then place them in a large bowl.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  Mash bananas using a hand mixer or fork.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  Add the egg  vegetable_oil  sugar  milk  and vanilla.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  Beat until combined.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  Sift the flour  baking_powder  baking_soda  and salt into the banana mixture.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  Beat until just combined  being careful to not overmix.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  Use a rubber spatula to gently fold the chocolate_sprinkles into the batter.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  Grease a 12-cup muffin tin with nonstick spray.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  Divide the batter among the cups.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  Bake for 20-25 minutes  until the tops are lightly browned and a toothpick inserted in the center of a muffin comes out clean.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  Place the chocolate chips in a heatproof liquid measuring cup.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  Pour over the hot heavy cream.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  Let sit for 1 minute  then stir until the chocolate is melted and smooth.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  While the muffins are still warm  use the back of a wooden spoon to push down a hole into the center of each muffin.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  Fill the muffins with the chocolate ganache.
In the recipe chocolate filled banana muffins  Chill the muffins in the fridge for at least 1 hour  until the center has set.
In the recipe chocolate fondue banana bread boat  In a large bowl  mash the bananas with a fork.
In the recipe chocolate fondue banana bread boat  Add in the oil  egg  sugar  and vanilla.
In the recipe chocolate fondue banana bread boat  Stir until combined.
In the recipe chocolate fondue banana bread boat  Add in the flour  baking_powder  baking_soda  salt  and cinnamon.
In the recipe chocolate fondue banana bread boat  Stir until just combined.
In the recipe chocolate fondue banana bread boat  Pour the banana bread batter into a greased loaf pan.
In the recipe chocolate fondue banana bread boat  In a small saucepan  combine the cream milk and chocolate  and melt over low heat.
In the recipe chocolate fondue banana bread boat  Add the vanilla and stir to combine.
In the recipe chocolate fondue banana bread boat  Let the banana bread cool in the pan for 30 minutes  then remove from the loaf pan and place on a serving dish.

In the recipe chocolate fondue banana bread boat  Using a knife cut a rectangle out of the top center of the loaf  leaving a 2- to 3-inch (5 cm to 7cm) perimeter of banana bread  making sure to not slice through the bread.
In the recipe chocolate fondue banana bread boat  Gently pull out each slice one at a time.
In the recipe chocolate fondue banana bread boat  Press the crumbs into the base of the cut out bread.
In the recipe chocolate fondue banana bread boat  Reheat the chocolate if needed then pour the chocolate into the banana bread boat.
In the recipe chocolate fondue banana bread boat  Place sliced bananas  strawberries  and the inside of the banana bread around the fondue boat.
In the recipe chocolate fondue banana bread boat  Enjoy!
